profile_positions.description:
• Support the team with daily operations and in maintaining an accurate payout process to our
customer - focus on Customer Centricity;
• Payment processing;
• Handling escalated payment related queries (emails and tickets) from Customer Service
globally - internal payment related inbound;
• Categorize tickets and analyze data on trends and main call drivers by tracking, and trending
payment issues;
• Taking part in various Deep Dive projects to analyze data to close gaps in the process.
• Handling incoming tickets, investigate and resolve the request by either approving or rejecting
the payout.
• All rejection payout required feedback on reasoning for rejection - decrease financial risk.
• Ensure internal control procedures are adhered to and are documented in accordance with
compliance standards- attention to financial data and details ie: currencies/amount;
• Ensure the accuracy of payments (required approvals, documentation, notes, procedures and
guidelines are in line with compliance and for audit purposes.
• Complete all tasks and payments in accordance with business policy and procedures.
